data.description: Contract Pending Discover your new home with this enchanting 3BR all-brick ranch, beautifully situated less than a block from the lush landscapes of Stransky Park. Freshly painted and boasting 1.75 bathrooms, it offers an irresistible blend of style and convenience. Outside, a covered patio and fenced yard await for your private outdoor escapes. This home holds potential for an easy duplex conversion, appealing to both homeowners and investors. This gem combines the tranquility of parkside living with the ease of city access. Make it yours and enjoy the best of both worlds.
